<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Reset */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #1e293b;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Container */
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Header */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }

        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        /* Content Area */
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0f172a;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Typography */
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #475569;
        }

        /* Call to Action */
        .cta-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
        }

        /* Cards/Sections */
        .section-card {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .section-title::before {
            content: "";
            display: inline-block;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: currentColor;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        /* Details */
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .detail-label {
            color: #64748b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .detail-value {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* OTP Code Style */
        .otp-box {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 2px dashed #0ea5e9;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .copyright {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                margin: 0;
                width: 100% !important;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Smart Clinic</h1>
            <p>{{#if subheader}}{{subheader}}{{else}}Chăm Sóc Sức Khỏe Toàn Diện{{/if}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            {{{body}}}
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Email này được gửi tự động từ hệ thống Smart Clinic.</p>
            <p>Vui lòng không trả lời trực tiếp email này.</p>
            <div class="copyright">
                &copy; 2026 Smart Clinic. Bảo lưu mọi quyền.
            </div>
            <p>Phòng khám Đa khoa Smart Clinic - Chăm sóc tận tâm, nâng tầm sức khỏe.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
